## Executive Summary


This document provides a detailed audit of the infrastructure and architecture for Forgotten Formula PMA's systems on March 10, 2026. It includes an analysis of simulated API error rates, system throughput monitoring, and recommendations for backend optimizations and database refactoring. This audit is conducted in alignment with our mission of prioritizing healing over profits and leveraging nature-first solutions.


